## Level 2 - Data Platform container

This level focuses on the system's high-level [containers](https://c4model.com/#ContainerDiagram), which are typically applications or services. It illustrates the major components of the system and their interactions. Web servers, databases, desktop and S3 buckets are all examples of containers.

